---
title: Classic Meatball Subs Trattoria Salad with Creamy Italian Dressing & Croutons
description: We’re channeling old-school vibes with this saucy meatball sub and salad that’s on your plate quicker than a trip to the Italian deli. Fully cooked beef meatballs are tossed with marinara sauce, sprinkled with melty mozzarella, and nestled into crusty baguettes. A crisp green salad with grape tomatoes and croutons makes it a meal.
